    <briefdescription>
<para>Storage manager for <ref refid="classhmap_1_1VirtualTexture" kindref="compound">VirtualTexture</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>A <ref refid="classhmap_1_1VirtualTexture" kindref="compound">VirtualTexture</ref> is composed of multiple VirtualArrays (channels). This storage wrapper ensures that each channel has a proper <ref refid="classhmap_1_1TileStorage" kindref="compound">TileStorage</ref> (RAM, DiskLRU, Sequential) and can manage shared directories, cleanup, etc. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
